l logistics park, centralized warehouse AMTZ; chartering services, cold chain and solutions, custom brokers, project logistics, rail logistics, and express movement logistics. The company was founded in 1867 and is based in Kolkata, India. Balmer Lawrie & Co. Ltd. is a subsidiary of Balmer Lawrie Investments Limited."}}